---
title: One-Pot Creamy Mushroom & Leek Risotto with Parmesan & Parsley
description: Mushrooms, we love those little meaty fungi found in fairytales so much that we’re bringing the magic out of the book straight
to your table! Pack them into a risotto with leek and carrot cooked in a creamy sauce. To finish with a happily-ever-after let’s
sprinkle over some fairy dust (also known as Parmesan cheese)!
